data.description: Situated within the serene Twin Lake North Condo community, this 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom unit offers an inviting open kitchen, a separate dining area, and a cozy screened-in porch extending from the living room. The primary bedroom boasts a 3/4 bath, complete with a convenient makeup counter and abundant closet space, with an additional bedroom or office and full bath.  Enjoy shared amenities such as a outdoor pool, sauna with locker room access. Added conveniences include heated underground parking and a dedicated storage locker. Nestled in a prime location, this condo affords easy access to nearby shopping centers, dining options, parks, and major highways, ensuring a seamless blend of comfort and convenience.  HOA includes gas, heat, trash removal, water, underground parking, cable tv.
